trans-unit.source: Represents a set of one or more <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment"></xref> elements.
A <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> element defines the structure and content of a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage>.
<xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> is the root of one or more <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragment> elements.

For detailed information about the document structure of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)], see Chapter 9 and Appendix E of the *XML Paper Specification (XPS)* that can be downloaded from the [Windows Hardware Developer Central](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761).
